air: verify directional rule at every coupling site\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.85,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Directional-mechanics verification and the absolute/relative correction are net-new; mild overlap with iter 1 structural foundation.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q2\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q2\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Apply forward/reverse hop-math uniformly to every deep-loop-* string\",\"reason\":\"WRONG for absolute literals (F2.3); classify relative-require vs absolute-literal first\",\"evidence\":\"deep-loop-runtime/scripts/compile-command-contracts.cjs:15-288\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:16:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":3,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"system-spec-kit tooling-borrow: verify both directions and re-path\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.6,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Borrow specifics and site-count correction are net-new, but path-mechanics build on iteration 2 directional reasoning, so overlap is higher.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q3\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q3\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Defer the borrow to child 003\",\"reason\":\"The live import at memory-runtime-retention.vitest.ts:9 fails at load time post-move; explicitly rejected by 002 §3\",\"evidence\":\"system-spec-kit/mcp_server/tests/memory-runtime-retention.vitest.ts:9\"}],\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"question\",\"id\":\"q3-borrow\",\"label\":\"Is the system-spec-kit tooling-borrow fully enumerated and correctly re-pathed?\"},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f3-1-forward\",\"label\":\"Forward borrow confirmed; one-more-.. correct\"},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f3-2-reverse\",\"label\":\"Reverse borrow confirmed; glob expansion correct\"},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f3-3-count\",\"label\":\"CORRECTION: borrow surface is ~6-8 sites not 4\"},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f3-4-activeimport\",\"label\":\"memory-runtime-retention import is active, raises severity above silent hole\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"from\":\"f3-1-forward\",\"to\":\"q3-borrow\",\"relation\":\"ANSWERS\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"from\":\"f3-4-activeimport\",\"to\":\"q3-borrow\",\"relation\":\"QUALIFIES\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:24:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-2/deep-research-state.jsonl"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-2/deep-research-state.jsonl","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-2/deep-research-state.jsonl","time":{"start":1783488732910,"end":1783488732912}},"id":"prt_f40365eec001q60bx59l1t4tmC","sessionID":"ses_0bfd3a445ffeKWJBUrOFOoCdGM","messageID":"msg_f403606c2001WaU4NnVuHdEjym"}}
