{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783488910975,"sessionID":"ses_0bfd3a445ffeKWJBUrOFOoCdGM","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_dfc7ad5cdbf341a184ca4aab","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"topic\":\"Validate and stress-test the merge design for folding deep-loop-runtime into deep-loop-workflows as system-deep-loop\",\"maxIterations\":5,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.05,\"stuckThreshold\":3,\"specFolder\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research\",\"executor\":{\"kind\":\"cli-opencode\",\"model\":\"zai-coding-plan/glm-5.2\",\"reasoningEffort\":\"max\"},\"lineage\":{\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm52-2-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"label\":\"glm52-2\",\"family\":\"glm52\"},\"createdAt\":\"2026-07-08T00:00:00Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"lineage_init\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm52-2-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"detachedLineage\":true,\"artifactDirOverride\":\".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-2\",\"resolveArtifactRootSkipped\":true,\"generation\":1,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:00:05Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":1,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Structural layout: verify child 002 §8 target layout against live trees\",\"findingsCount\":4,\"newInfoRatio\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"First pass; all findings new to this packet. Layout correctness is load-bearing for all subsequent questions.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q1\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q1\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Split runtime lib across the four mode packets\",\"reason\":\"Would destroy the one-frozen-backend invariant both SKILL.md files narrate\",\"evidence\":\"deep-loop-workflows/SKILL.md:12,112,138\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:08:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":2,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Bidirectional path-coupling repair: verify directional rule at every coupling site\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.85,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Directional-mechanics verification and the absolute/relative correction are net-new; mild overlap with iter 1 structural foundation.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q2\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q2\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Apply forward/reverse hop-math uniformly to every deep-loop-* string\",\"reason\":\"WRONG for absolute literals (F2.3); classify relative-require vs absolute-literal first\",\"evidence\":\"deep-loop-runtime/scripts/compile-command-contracts.cjs:15-288\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:16:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":3,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"system-spec-kit tooling-borrow: verify both directions and re-path\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.6,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Borrow specifics and site-count correction are net-new, but path-mechanics build on iteration 2 directional reasoning, so overlap is higher.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q3\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q3\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Defer the borrow to child 003\",\"reason\":\"The live import at memory-runtime-retention.vitest.ts:9 fails at load time post-move; explicitly rejected by 002 §3\",\"evidence\":\"system-spec-kit/mcp_server/tests/memory-runtime-retention.vitest.ts:9\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:24:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":4,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"External reference migration and advisor corpus (highest-risk surface)\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":0.45,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Advisor-corpus details (runtime-target anomaly, parity-test volume, drift-guard self-reference) are net-new and decision-relevant, but the overall reference-migration pattern is familiar from iters 2-3.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q4\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q4\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Blind whole-file find/replace across the advisor corpus\",\"reason\":\"Destroys reviewed reason narration and mishandles the runtime-target anomaly (F4.3)\",\"evidence\":\"local-native-approved-divergences.json:530\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:32:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":5,\"status\":\"insight\",\"focus\":\"Fallback-router wiring: confirm zero live callers, decide wire-vs-defer\",\"findingsCount\":5,\"newInfoRatio\":0.2,\"noveltyJustification\":\"Mostly confirms what 004 documents; net-new is the defer-recommendation rationale and merge-stable import confirmation. All key questions answered.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"Q5\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Q5\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Wire fallback-router into the 002/003 merge as a bonus\",\"reason\":\"Scope creep; merge must be clean verifiable rename+nesting, new runtime behavior ships separately\",\"evidence\":\"004/spec.md:42-48,90-96\"}],\"convergenceSignals\":{\"rollingAvg\":0.42,\"madScore\":0.12,\"entropyCoverage\":1.0,\"compositeStop\":0.74},\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:40:00Z\",\"durationMs\":480000}\n{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"convergence_eval\",\"mode\":\"research\",\"run\":5,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-glm52-2-1783486518892-2qss01\",\"stopReason\":\"converged\",\"stopCandidate\":true,\"gates\":{\"convergence\":\"pass\",\"coverage\":\"pass\",\"quality\":\"pass\",\"graph\":\"pass\"},\"compositeStop\":0.74,\"avgNewInfoRatio\":0.62,\"questionsAnsweredRatio\":1.0,\"minIterationsFloor\":3,\"minIterationsSatisfied\":true,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-08T00:41:00Z\"}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-2/deep-research-state.jsonl"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/052-deep-loop-unification/001-reference-research/research/lineages/glm52-2/deep-research-state.jsonl","exis